data.description: St. Louis Park mid-century rambler features a living room, eat in kitchen, and 3 bedrooms on the main level.  Finished lower level has 4th bedroom (with egress), full bath, great room, and flex space (gym/crafting/workshop). Front patio with 9 X 9 pergola included.  Neighborhood conveniently close to grocery, shopping, restaurants, and easy access to major transportation routes.
